  <data key="d0">ORGANIZATION</data>
  <data key="d1">A company committed to sustainability and contributing to societal well-being.&lt;SEP&gt;A company focused on advanced manufacturing with a commitment to risk management strategies such as diversifying customer base and maintaining adequate cash reserves.&lt;SEP&gt;A company involved in advanced manufacturing solutions.&lt;SEP&gt;A company noted for its strong financial performance and dividend distribution to shareholders.&lt;SEP&gt;A company that undertook significant corporate governance developments and initiatives in 2017 to enhance transparency, accountability, and stakeholder engagement.&lt;SEP&gt;A manufacturing company that underwent financial developments and strategic initiatives in 2017.&lt;SEP&gt;A manufacturing solutions provider that acquired a stake in Precision Components Ltd.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc. is a company implementing financial strategies focused on cost control and capital operations for growth and profitability.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc. is a publicly listed manufacturing company established on August 15, 2005 in Cityville, Techland, specializing in the design, development, and manufacturing of high-tech precision tools and equipment for various industries.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc. is an organization that established an Ethics Committee and published a Sustainability Report.&lt;SEP&gt;Advanced Manufacturing Solutions Inc. successfully executed a debt restructuring process and declared dividend distribution in July 2017.</data>
